com.itko.lisaint.ejb

Class EJBIntegrator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.itko.lisaint.Integrator
      • com.itko.lisaint.java.JavaIntegrator
        • com.itko.lisaint.ejb.EJBIntegrator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class EJBIntegrator
extends JavaIntegrator
    The EJBIntegrator is a subclass of the JavaIntegrator. It provides any needed specialization of the Lisa Integrator support when running in an EJB application. You will generally only need to interact with the HasLisaIntegrator interface and the Integrator methods.
    See Also:
    HasLisaIntegrator, Integrator, Serialized Form
